  story {
    writer {
      name: "Sukumar"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The concept is pretty interesting as it is a character based movie that follows his hero's journey; the plot structure is pretty standard for a hero's journey movie, but the ending feels a bit unnecessary; character writing is good for Pushpa as this movie creates a very iconic character to start this character-driven action franchise"
  }
  screenplay {
    writer {
      name: "Sukumar"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Good"
    comments: "The dialogue is filled with a lot of iconic dialogue that makes this a blockbuster action movie; the humor is pretty good as it interjects the movie's seriousness to make this a unique movie; the symbolism is decently prevelant as the movie talks about themes like family and the importance of your name; the foreshadowing is decent"
  }
