  pacing: "Pacing is on the slower side as it feels like the story is dragging a little bit"
  climax: "Climax is a little unnecessary, as they added a new storyline with like 20 minutes left in the movie; this new storyline has nothing to do with the original storyline and is more for building up the sequel"
  tone: "Tone is very action-Tollywood"
  final_notes: ""
  overall: "Overall, a character-driven action Tollywood movie that is carried by pretty good writing and a good performance from Allu Arjun to create this iconic character, Pushpa; the story does feel a bit bloated as the final 20 minutes really do not have anything to do with the original story"
